<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.3.4">
<l>vāmpa riyuka maṉṉarta muyirceka vaivarkaṭ karacaḷitta</l>
<l>kāmpi ṉārtiru vēṅkaṭap poruppaniṉ kātalai yaruḷeṉakku</l>
<l>māmpo ḻiltaḷir kōtiya maṭakkuyil vāyatu tuvarppeyta</l>
<l>tīmpa laṅkaṉit tēṉatu nukartiru veḷḷaṟai niṉṟāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Ruler of sacred Vēṅkaṭa [Mountain] covered with bamboo</l>
<l rend="indent">who granted a kingdom to the Five</l>
<l>When [you] destroyed the kings’ lives as leaping horses fell,</l>
<l rend="indent">[graciously] grant your love to me,</l>
<l>[Lord] who stands in Tiruveḷḷaṟai where the simple cuckoo,</l>
<l rend="indent">which had pecked at shoots in the mango grove,</l>
<l>When it’s mouth got bitter, relished the sweet nectar of the jackfruit.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
